headline: VRSN Q1 Earnings Call: Domain Growth and Dividend Initiation Highlight Strategic Shift
summary: Domain name registry operator Verisign (NASDAQ:VRSN) met Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q1 CY2025, with sales up 4.7% year on year to $402.3 million. Its GAAP profit of $2.10 per share was in line with analysts’ consensus estimates.
